spec_data.Name: perl-Net-Netmask
spec_data.Description:
Net::Netmask parses and understands IPv4 CIDR blocks. It's built with
an object-oriented interface. Nearly all functions are methods that
operate on a Net::Netmask object.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:30:07 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Perl module for manipulation and lookup of IP network blocks
